messages.message:
In prepare for migrating our UAT and dogfood environment to AWS from GCP, we are conducting a survey to get more insight on what needs to migrated from the existing environments and make sure our testing won't be negatively affected by this migration, I created a new run in testmo with name "UAT AWS migration planning" (https://instabase.testmo.net/runs/view/48?group_id=1) and `you don't need to conduct the actual testing, just mark it pass if you think the test does not depend on any data existing in current dogfood/UAT,  if they do, please reach out to #team-release-eng and let us know what we need to migrate`, thanks!
cc @shaunak @Kerry @andy @lydia @Aaron Tami this should be a quick action and appreciate if you can help making time for your team to do this :pray:
